subtitleNullable: 62 class Traffic sign data for classification with .PPM files
descriptionNullable:
### Context

The data-set contains Belgium Traffic Sign image data with 62 class (0 to 61) which can be used for image classification using CNN model.


### Content

Images are in  .PPM file which is a 24-bit color image formatted using a text format. It stores each pixel with a number from 0 to 65536, which specifies the color of the pixel. PPM files also store the image height and width, white space data, and the maximum color value.
